Class Starship

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment1.problem2.AbstractStarship
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FirstOrder, Resistance

    public class Starship
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by timzyt on 09/12/2018. super class which constructs and initiates a generic Starship with its organization, the destroy status, fuel level. Starship class also uses to implement fuel and attack methods.
